Package: chess2plyrs
Type: Package
Title: Chess Game and Tools in R
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Luigi", "Annicchiarico", email = "luigi.annic@gmail.com", role = c("cre", "aut"))
    )
Description: Chess package written in base R. The program allows the user to create a game, add moves,
             check for legal moves and game result, plot the board, take back, read and write FEN.
             A basic chess engine are implemented.
Depends:
    R (>= 4.3.0)
Imports: 
    stats,
    ggplot2 (>= 3.4.4)
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Suggests: 
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
VignetteBuilder: knitr
